text: Grønning is a small village in the municipality of Hadsel in Nordland county, Norway. Grønning may also refer to: * Grønning Church, in the village of Grønning * Jeppe Grønning (born 1991), Danish professional footballer * Pia Grønning (born 1949), Danish film actor who has also performed in Hollywood movies * Sebastian Grønning (born 1997), Danish footballer ==See also== * Grønn, a surname * Category:Surnames of Danish origin
